<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-109-216 </DOCNO><DOCID>10 961 454</DOCID><JOURNAL>PC Week  July 8 1991 v8 n27 p45(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Ziff-Davis Publishing Co. 1991.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Telebit server gets security system, remote card keys. (ExtendedUser Authentication) (product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Zimmerman, Michael R.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Telebit Corp. (Product introduction).andO;Ticker:    TBIT.andO;Product:   Telebit Extended User Authentication (Data Security Equipment)(Product introduction).andO;Topic:     Data securityProduct Introduction.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>By Michael R. ZimmermanandM;Telebit Corp. recently buttressed the security of its asynchronouscommunications server with caller-authentication features and remote cardkeys.andM;Dubbed EUA (Extended User Authentication), the optional hardware/softwaresystem governs access to the ACS by demanding specific information fromremote callers who attempt to dial in -- for example, a personalidentification number or a return phone number, officials said.andP;  Whenequipped with EUA, the ACS, which serves as a modem-sharing device for LANs,will not permit callers to log on to the network if they fail to answer anyquestions correctly.andM;EUA, which comprises a federally approved data-encryption board that fitsinto the ACS and software, is priced at $995 for an Industry StandardArchitecture (ISA) version and $1,195 for a Micro Channel release.andM;For security beyond EUA, Telebit offers RemoteKeys priced at $150 apiece,said William Botti, general manager of the communications products divisionfor the Sunnyvale, Calif., company.andP;  These pocket calculatorlike devicesdeliver encrypted responses to ACS questions, which the remote user mustenter when trying to access the server.andM;Telebit, one of the leaders in the modem field with more than $42 million inrevenue last year, extended its product line with the ACS last month.andP;  Thefirm's communications offerings are available through authorized computerdealers and distributors.andP;  Telebit can be reached at (800) 835-3248.andO;</TEXT></DOC>